# Interface ElevenLabsOutputFormatInterface

Interface for ElevenLabs output format configuration.

interface ElevenLabsOutputFormatInterface {  
outputFormat?:  
| "MP3_22050_32"  
| "MP3_44100_32"  
| "MP3_44100_64"  
| "MP3_44100_96"  
| "MP3_44100_128"  
| "MP3_44100_192";  
}
